| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6194 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2d4b49ce-eec4-5c8f-921f-6af83c579c6d"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
